!ml/evaluation/fixtures/*.csv
# keep the data/raw README tracked (real odds CSVs dropped here stay ignored):
!data/raw/README.md

# Generated by pipeline/fit_attack_defence.py (offline fit). The Phase-5 gate
# was REFUTED (docs/MODEL-EXPERIMENTS.md), so the store does NOT ship; if a
# future gate run clears, force-add the fitted file with the params flag flip.
ml/models/team_offsets.json

# StatsBomb open-data event/match cache for pipeline/backfill_xg.py — ~314
# match blobs fetched on demand, never committed.
pipeline/data/statsbomb_cache/

